:

1. *Pamet* je najvrednije bogatstvo. (Wisdom is the most valuable wealth.)
2. On je uvek bio *pametan*. (He was always wise.)
3. On se oslanja na svoju *pamet*. (He relies on his wisdom.)
4. Nije mudro koristiti *pamet* kao oru≈æje. (It is not wise to use wisdom as a weapon.)
5. On je pokazao *pamet* u odluci. (He showed wisdom in the decision.)
6. *Pametno* je doneti odluke sa razumom. (It is wise to make decisions with reason.)